title: Batman Beyond 2.0 complete to date (revised to issue 26 (darkhom
description:
This is a request by a member here.  While I am more able to provide current issues, IF I can find what you are looking for I will try and post it for you.  Nemesis43 on KAT has far more resources than I and is a better bet, but I will do what I can to help the communities.  Please message me privately for requests so as not to clutter up comment sections with unrelated material.







This torrent is an update to the previous verion I uploaded in March.  It includes the 26 issues released for Batman Beyond 2.0.  It's a brand new day for Terry McGinnis! Now enrolled at Neo-Gotham University, Terry struggles with his new life as a college student while maintaining Bruce Wayne's legacy as the Batman of the future. But a new school isn't the ONLY change for our hero...
